Antennules (Fig. 8C) similar to preceding species except for not extending beyond distal margin of fifth pedigerous somite and for failure to express an aesthetasc on ancestral segments VI, VIII, composite X-XI, XX and XIII. In addition, the composite segment I-II displays 4 setae (vs. 3 in 
